title: Babyname
description: Babyname is the new way for you and your partner to find the perfect name for your baby. Connect with your partner and swipe through baby name cards together. If you both like the same name, it's a match and is added to your favorites list, so you'll never forget it. Yay! Apple's top parenting apps: itunes.apple.com/us/story/id1345383815
